    {
      "id": "city_god_altar",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "香案",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": 502.2,
      "interactionRange": 128.6,
      "data": {
        "text": "香案上只剩些断香和灰烬。城隍爷的泥身斑驳得厉害，半边脸都裂开了，看着比庙外的夜色还阴。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "hide_iron_box",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "城隍像后的暗角",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": 279,
      "interactionRange": 128.6,
      "conditions": [
        {
          "flag": "got_iron_box"
        },
        {
          "flag": "box_hidden_in_temple",
          "op": "!=",
          "value": true
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "城隍像后头积了厚厚一层灰，砖缝里正好塞得下一只半巴掌大的铁盒。你左右看看，咬咬牙，把盒子推进去藏好了。",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "setFlag",
            "params": {
              "key": "box_hidden_in_temple",
              "value": true
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "startCutscene",
            "params": {
              "id": "temple_strangers_arrive"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "moonlit_wall",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "墙边月影",
      "x": 1571.4,
      "y": 669.6,
      "interactionRange": 185.7,
      "conditions": [
        {
          "flag": "strangers_entered_temple"
        },
        {
          "flag": "saw_standing_shadow",
          "op": "!=",
          "value": true
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "你屏着气，又慢慢摸回庙门口。月光从屋顶的破洞漏下来，斜斜照在墙上。墙边明明该趴着一具倒地的人影，可你看见的，却是个直挺挺站着的女人影子。\n\n你头皮一炸，连盒子都不敢再想，转身就跑，直到冲回街巷才敢喘气。今晚这事，怎么都得等天亮以后再回来看个明白。",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "setFlag",
            "params": {
              "key": "saw_standing_shadow",
              "value": true
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "setFlag",
            "params": {
              "key": "first_night_escape",
              "value": true
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "switchScene",
            "params": {
              "targetScene": "test_room_a",
              "targetSpawnPoint": "from_temple"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "hanged_woman_day2",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "梁下",
      "x": 1000,
      "y": 669.6,
      "interactionRange": 142.9,
      "conditions": [
        {
          "flag": "day_2_started"
        },
        {
          "flag": "saw_hanged_woman",
          "op": "!=",
          "value": true
        }
      ],
      "data": {
        "text": "你抬头一看，浑身都僵了。梁上吊着一具女尸，正是昨晚那女人。她脸朝外，舌头微微伸着，眼珠子已经不会动了。\n\n你强撑着挪开眼，往城隍像后头摸——砖缝里的铁盒还在。你一把抓起来揣进怀里，头也不回地冲出了庙门。",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "setFlag",
            "params": {
              "key": "saw_hanged_woman",
              "value": true
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "startCutscene",
            "params": {
              "id": "prologue_demo_end"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "stone_tablet",
      "type": "inspect",
      "label": "石碑",
      "x": 428.6,
      "y": 390.6,
      "interactionRange": 114.3,
      "data": {
        "text": "角落里立着块旧石碑，碑文风化得只剩最后几句还能认：\"阎王岭下，阴阳交汇，城隍镇之。\"你看完只觉背后更凉了。",
        "actions": [
          {
            "type": "setFlag",
            "params": {
              "key": "inspected_stone_tablet",
              "value": true
            }
          },
          {
            "type": "addArchiveEntry",
            "params": {
              "bookType": "lore",
              "entryId": "lore_temple_history"
            }
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
